# Project Structure Guide

This is a Spring Boot based resume management system with a frontend built using vanilla JavaScript.

## Key Files and Directories

### Backend Structure
- [src/main/java/com/shechubbb/web/resume/ResumeApplication.java](mdc:src/main/java/com/shechubbb/web/resume/ResumeApplication.java) - Main application entry point
- [src/main/resources/application.properties](mdc:src/main/resources/application.properties) - Application configuration
- [src/main/resources/init.sql](mdc:src/main/resources/init.sql) - Database initialization script

### Frontend Structure
- [src/main/resources/static/index.html](mdc:src/main/resources/static/index.html) - User-facing resume page
- [src/main/resources/static/admin/index.html](mdc:src/main/resources/static/admin/index.html) - Admin dashboard
- [src/main/resources/static/js/resume.js](mdc:src/main/resources/static/js/resume.js) - User frontend logic
- [src/main/resources/static/admin/js/admin.js](mdc:src/main/resources/static/admin/js/admin.js) - Admin dashboard logic

### CSS Structure
- [src/main/resources/static/css/variables.css](mdc:src/main/resources/static/css/variables.css) - Theme variables
- [src/main/resources/static/css/base.css](mdc:src/main/resources/static/css/base.css) - Base styles
- [src/main/resources/static/css/sections.css](mdc:src/main/resources/static/css/sections.css) - Resume sections styles
- [src/main/resources/static/admin/css/style.css](mdc:src/main/resources/static/admin/css/style.css) - Admin dashboard styles
